          "&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total amount to be divided = ₹4,800&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Ratio among Ram, Shyam, and Kartik = 4 : 8 : 3&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula Used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Amount received by each = (Individual&amp;#39;s ratio / Sum of ratios) &amp;times; Total amount&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Sum of ratios = 4 + 8 + 3&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Sum of ratios = 15&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Amount received by Shyam = (Shyam&amp;#39;s ratio / Sum of ratios) &amp;times; Total amount&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Amount received by Shyam = (8 / 15) &amp;times; ₹4,800&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Amount received by Shyam = ₹(8 &amp;times; 4,800) / 15&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Amount received by Shyam = ₹38,400 / 15&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Amount received by Shyam = ₹2,560&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Therefore, the amount received by Shyam is ₹2,560.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n",
