          "&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Average age of 30 students = 18 years&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;When teacher&amp;#39;s age is included, the average age of the group = 18 + 1 = 19 years&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total number of individuals in the group = 30 + 1 = 31&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula Used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total age = Average age &amp;times; Total number of individuals&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Teacher&amp;#39;s age = Total age (with teacher) - Total age (without teacher)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total age of 30 students = 18 &amp;times; 30&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total age of 30 students = 540&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total age of group (with teacher) = 19 &amp;times; 31&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Total age of group (with teacher) = 589&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Teacher&amp;#39;s age = Total age (with teacher) - Total age (without teacher)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Teacher&amp;#39;s age = 589 - 540&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Teacher&amp;#39;s age = 49&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The teacher&amp;#39;s age is 49 years.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n",
